%e A079859 a(4)=4 since the palindromic compositions of 7 that contain a 3 are 2+3+2, 1+1+3+1+1 and 3+1+3, for a total of 4 3s. The palindromic compositions of 8 that contain a 4 are 2+4+2, 1+1+4+1+1 and 4+4.
